Maintainer: Xiaofeng Wu <1427972815@qq.com>
Description: This package specializes in analyzing and visualizing eQTL at the single-cell level. 
    It can read gene expression matrices or Seurat data, along with genotype data. 
    It offers a function for cis-eQTL analysis to detect eQTL within a given range, and another function to fit models with three methods. 
    Using this package, users can also generate single-cell level visualization result.
